---
// AgentLoop.astro — Animated agent reasoning loop showing Think → Act → Observe cycle
---

<div class="al-wrap">
  <h3 class="al-title">The Agent Loop: Think → Act → Observe → Repeat</h3>
  <p class="al-sub">Every AI agent follows this cycle. The loop is the intelligence.</p>

  <div class="al-loop">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 280" class="al-svg">
      <!-- Center label -->
      <text x="200" y="136" fill="#64748b" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">AGENT LOOP</text>
      <text x="200" y="150" fill="#475569" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">repeats until done</text>

      <!-- Think node -->
      <g class="al-node al-node--think">
        <rect x="140" y="20" width="120" height="50" rx="12" fill="rgba(129,140,248,0.1)" stroke="#818cf840" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="200" y="42" fill="#818cf8" font-size="11" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">THINK</text>
        <text x="200" y="58" fill="#64748b" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">Plan next action</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Act node -->
      <g class="al-node al-node--act">
        <rect x="270" y="115" width="120" height="50" rx="12" fill="rgba(74,222,128,0.1)" stroke="#4ade8040" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="330" y="137" fill="#4ade80" font-size="11" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">ACT</text>
        <text x="330" y="153" fill="#64748b" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">Call a tool</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Observe node -->
      <g class="al-node al-node--observe">
        <rect x="140" y="210" width="120" height="50" rx="12" fill="rgba(245,158,11,0.1)" stroke="#f59e0b40" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="200" y="232" fill="#f59e0b" font-size="11" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">OBSERVE</text>
        <text x="200" y="248" fill="#64748b" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">Check result</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Decide node -->
      <g class="al-node al-node--decide">
        <rect x="10" y="115" width="120" height="50" rx="12" fill="rgba(6,182,212,0.1)" stroke="#06b6d440" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="70" y="137" fill="#06b6d4" font-size="11" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">DECIDE</text>
        <text x="70" y="153" fill="#64748b" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" font-family="monospace">Done or loop?</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Arrows -->
      <path d="M260 50 Q300 50 300 115" fill="none" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="4,3" marker-end="url(#al-arrow)"/>
      <path d="M300 165 Q300 230 260 235" fill="none" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="4,3" marker-end="url(#al-arrow)"/>
      <path d="M140 235 Q100 235 100 165" fill="none" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="4,3" marker-end="url(#al-arrow)"/>
      <path d="M100 115 Q100 50 140 45" fill="none" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="4,3" marker-end="url(#al-arrow)"/>

      <defs>
        <marker id="al-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto">
          <path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="#475569"/>
        </marker>
      </defs>

      <!-- Orbiting dot -->
      <circle r="5" fill="#f472b6">
        <animateMotion dur="4s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M200,45 Q300,45 300,140 Q300,235 200,235 Q100,235 100,140 Q100,45 200,45" />
      </circle>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="al-steps">
    <div class="al-step-card al-sc--purple">
      <span class="al-sc-num">1</span>
      <span class="al-sc-text"><strong>Think:</strong> "I need to look up the user's order status. I'll call the orders API."</span>
    </div>
    <div class="al-step-card al-sc--green">
      <span class="al-sc-num">2</span>
      <span class="al-sc-text"><strong>Act:</strong> Calls get_order_status(order_id="12345")</span>
    </div>
    <div class="al-step-card al-sc--amber">
      <span class="al-sc-num">3</span>
      <span class="al-sc-text"><strong>Observe:</strong> API returns "shipped, tracking: UPS1234, arrives Thursday"</span>
    </div>
    <div class="al-step-card al-sc--cyan">
      <span class="al-sc-num">4</span>
      <span class="al-sc-text"><strong>Decide:</strong> "I have what I need. Format the answer and respond."</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .al-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .al-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .al-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .al-loop { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #334155; padding: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .al-svg { width: 100%; max-width: 400px; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }

  .al-node { opacity: 0; animation: alNodeIn 0.5s ease-out forwards; }
  .al-node--think { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .al-node--act { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .al-node--observe { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .al-node--decide { animation-delay: 1.1s; }

  .al-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; }

  .al-step-card {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 12px; border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .al-sc--purple { border-left: 3px solid #818cf830; }
  .al-sc--green { border-left: 3px solid #4ade8030; }
  .al-sc--amber { border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b30; }
  .al-sc--cyan { border-left: 3px solid #06b6d430; }

  .al-sc-num {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 800; font-family: monospace;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #94a3b8;
  }
  .al-sc-text { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.7rem; line-height: 1.5; }
  .al-sc-text strong { color: #e2e8f0; }

  @keyframes alNodeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(5px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
</style>
